item.description:
Gnome Configurations # Disable wayland # Edit /etc/gdm/custom.conf as follows.
- #WaylandEnable=false + WaylandEnable=false + DefaultSession=gnome-xorg.desktop Otherwise run /usr/lib/gdm-disable-wayland as root.
sudo /usr/lib/gdm-disable-wayland Turn off alert # dconf write /org/gnome/desktop/sound/event-sounds &#34;false&#34;
